metadata.name: ELAINE BAG #2
metadata.description:
ELAINE BAG


The Elaine Bag is a tote bag handmade in New York City. The bag features an open design, top handles, and an exterior pocket. Each Elaine Bag has the NFSHE logo and is distinguished by the unique number embroidered on the top left corner of the exterior pocket. This number indicates the order in which the bag was produced. 



Perks & Utility:


TOTE BAG

Receive the physical Elaine Bag

- Features: handmade, 100% organic cotton canvas, webbing straps, 1 exterior pocket, open top, embroidery of the NFSHE logo and unique bag number

- Dimensions: 10in W x 4in D x 8in H, 5in strap drop


RARITY

Each Elaine Bag is uniquely numbered by production order


COMMUNITY

Gain entry to the NFSHE holder community



Policy:

All sales are final. Only primary sales are eligible for the physical NFSHE product
